{"tid":2286892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國金89樓】許正宇騎劫積金局助MPF送中 - 程總裁","createTime":"2020-11-15T10:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T04:59:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"deeac43da03f60500ba52d3ab742ff1e547b214b","tid":2286892,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201115/VEBKI6KKFRBQRB5COBG2XGRFSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201115%2FVEBKI6KKFRBQRB5COBG2XGRFSA%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=48c6371e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201115%2FVEBKI6KKFRBQRB5COBG2XGRFSA%2F&h=8483c4d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201115/VEBKI6KKFRBQRB5COBG2XGRFSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【國金89樓】許正宇騎劫積金局助MPF送中 - 程總裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U1UBUKM1i5Z4hbWYHJvFbxfqsPU=/6240x3704/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I26Z4MIX2RHKVCSMZPZA2TESGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU1UBUKM1i5Z4hbWYHJvFbxfqsPU%3D%2F6240x3704%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI26Z4MIX2RHKVCSMZPZA2TESGM.jpg&h=37648648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■財庫局局長許正宇。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n強積金關乎市民退休生活，可投資的資產有一定制約，以管理風險，這個正常不過，是故滬深兩間證券交易所持倉上限僅為10%，原因就是中國資本市場未完全開放，就算滬港通、深港通啟動多年，積金局過去多年仍然重申條件未成熟。<br />\n<br />\n不過財庫局局長許正宇在其Blog一聲令下，滬深交易所成為強積金「核准交易所」，10%上限緊箍咒消失，難道許局長收到中國資本賬開放的絕密消息？如果不是，那轉捩點是甚麼？買賣股票流動性風險如何remedy？。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大佬，。。。。。。。。。。。。局長一定係幫佢哋注射咗豬激素，所以熟得咁快？<br />\n<br />\n積金局之後回應亦搞笑，解釋滬深交易所獲納入，係根據「最近一次檢視和評核，並參照一籃子關乎交易所的具體因素和市場因素的審核準則」，請問即是甚麼因素、甚麼準則？更有趣嘅係，早年積金局主席黃友嘉解釋過A股遲遲未完全開通，係因為業界需求不大，想投資中國亦可以買H股。係啊，許局長都自爆A股只佔強積金總資產1.12%，<span class=\"orange\">乜近排打工仔突然對A股需求大咗咩？定其實係A股對強積金需求大咗，要拎香港市民血汗錢去托市？</span><br />\n<br />\n許局長唔只幫大家開咗條退休金送中渠道，仲送埋去波蘭同印尼！華沙證券交易所上市公司總市值只係約1萬億港元，印尼證券交易所市值亦只係3萬億港元，但獲納入「核准交易所」原因同兩間分別幾十萬億元市值嘅交易所一致，政策可謂毫無邏輯可言。<br />\n<br />\n其實積金局。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n程總裁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/IFC89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FIFC89&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=7aa99825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/IFC89</a>"},{"pid":"0a82eabca0afb447dd1c2cadeb915a1a530bdcd2","tid":2286892,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"你咪轉 MPF 去北美股票基金囉"},{"pid":"b5445995631c85df7b52dc2718b495ef51ac0d02","tid":2286892,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0a82eabca0afb447dd1c2cadeb915a1a530bdcd2","tid":2286892,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"你咪轉 MPF 去北美股票基金囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"北美都好多老千股。"},{"pid":"c02da72f88afd30aef4635cd7b0b1b471592380d","tid":2286892,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"講真而家港股同買支那股有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a5001a44ba450c5abcc496b7141cbe4b356cdb","tid":2286892,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5445995631c85df7b52dc2718b495ef51ac0d02","tid":2286892,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0a82eabca0afb447dd1c2cadeb915a1a530bdcd2","tid":2286892,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"你咪轉 MPF 去北美股票基金囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"北美都好多老千股。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"有好多都買返好多qq 阿里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc84603de73e1e4e13a5fa13fe17c9e001257a3","tid":2286892,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":